      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "An exceptional classic in truly outstanding condition, this car is the kind of example that\u2019s getting harder and harder to find. It presents beautifully throughout, has clearly been cared for to a very high standard, and is ready to impress whether you want to show it, collect it, or simply enjoy it. If you\u2019ve been waiting for a top-quality vintage car with real presence and no excuses, this one is absolutely worth a look.",
