      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle is a practical choice for someone seeking low-cost transportation or a project opportunity. It offers solid value for the price point and a chance to get into a vehicle without a major investment. Priced to reflect its condition while still presenting an appealing budget-conscious option.",
