      "description": "Looking for a cheap runabout or a solid project? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, drives, and still has plenty to offer someone who wants affordable wheels without a lot of fuss. Great option for a first car, a backup vehicle, or someone handy who enjoys bringing a car back to its best. Priced fairly and represented honestly\u2014come take a look and see if it\u2019s the right fit for you.",
      "price": 6800.0,
