      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver/project with strong old-school character. The engine starts up and pulls with respectable torque, the transmission engages as it should, and the chassis feels like a great foundation for someone who appreciates a straightforward, mechanical setup. It shows cosmetic wear and age-related flaws, but that also means you can get into it without paying a premium. Great candidate for a dependable beater, weekend tinkering, or a light restoration. Priced to move for someone who knows what they\u2019re looking at.",
      "price": 6900.0,
